  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0bc2.19 \u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0ba4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba8\u0b95\u0bc8, \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Gold jewelery and coins worth Rs 19 crore recovered",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Two Indians and a Sri Lankan were arrested at the Katunayake Bandaranaike International Airport along with gold jewellery, gold biscuits and foreign currency worth Rs 19 crore, airport customs officials said.",
        "The suspects arrived in the country by flights that arrived from Dubai last night (03) and New Delhi early today (04).",
        "A search conducted on the persons revealed 8.5 kilograms of gold jewellery, two halved gold biscuits, USD 75,000 and EUR 18,000.",
        "The customs officials said that the trio had concealed the items in their clothes and the specially designed shoes they were wearing.",
        "The Indians, aged 42 and 53, were found to be involved in gold and currency smuggling between India and Sri Lanka, while the 46-year-old Sri Lankan was a frequent foreign visitor for business purposes.",
        "The seized gold and foreign currency were confiscated and the three persons were fined Rs 25,000 each."
      ],
